3d376d2221" class="r-hsnvxs"><div data-rid="db42c783-8f48-40e7-8106-8eb4aba4d969" class="r-1q7i93o alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes! The Clear Skin Kit is designed to target all types of acne, including hormonal breakouts. It’s a unique 3-step routine that works to deeply clean skin without stripping, intensely moisturize with barrier boosting ingredients and treat hormonal acne with an anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial oil that can penetrate beyond the top layer of your skin to beat hormonal acne before it ever comes to a head.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="39aba9b2-dace-41a9-87a5-93613cda87d9" class="r-1h2mw0t" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="3f9539d6-25ee-4bc5-bb9d-e0ad063b2e5d" aria-controls="replo-:Reqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-i45kis"><div data-rid="d95f757f-05dd-449c-bf40-2c5fc206a5fd" class="r-1g37ar0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What types of acne does the Clear Skin Kit work on?</p></span></div><div data-rid="c6954d18-a362-49ca-85aa-7eb12019833e" class="r-13moq1s"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-ondb8m" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:Reqb2:"><div data-rid="ed8c253c-00e8-424a-844e-c12a5006e4f1" class="r-1vyoarh"><div data-rid="8e0be6bf-1e80-481c-a8ed-308b11c1ee80" class="r-mzzx9b alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The Clear Skin Kit is formulated to target a wide range of acne types, including:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hormonal acne</strong> – those deep, cystic breakouts that tend to pop up around your jawline, chin, or during your cycle</p></li><li><p><strong>Whiteheads & blackheads</strong> – caused by clogged pores and excess oil</p></li><li><p><strong>Inflamed pimples</strong> – red, tender spots that are painful to the touch</p></li><li><p><strong>Congestion-prone skin</strong> – areas with tiny bumps, texture, or under-the-skin breakouts<br><br></p></li></ul><p>The kit works by combining gentle exfoliation, anti-inflammatory ingredients, and deeply hydrating formulas to clear breakouts <em>without</em> stripping your skin. It's especially effective for people who deal with recurring or stubborn acne, and it’s safe for sensitive or reactive skin types.</p><p>Whether your breakouts are hormonal, stress-induced, or from environmental triggers — this routine helps reset your skin barrier, unclog pores, and keep future flare-ups in check.</p><p><br></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="cad04374-01fc-465f-8e53-e2dfb18f275a" class="r-xat8v" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="820e8270-19d2-4ef3-b124-eeaa2ba0caf0" aria-controls="replo-:Riqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-6zxzb8"><div data-rid="c4b64b73-946f-463e-b45d-c46c149f1ef4" class="r-w8vcgm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What age is Blume suited for?</p></span></div><div data-rid="89446fa4-09d4-448d-a404-642b8f93f0f4" class="r-x9n51s"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1ha9ou" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:Riqb2:"><div data-rid="e186475b-e3a3-46e4-ba99-5fc7c1c85a1c" class="r-bbcoc6"><div data-rid="800f01e5-96b0-4d27-bf43-61d5d10e4dd3" class="r-1hx7ztb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Blume is great for teens, young adults, and anyone with sensitive, acne-prone skin. It can be used for as young as 7 years old, up until 100! Our formulas are gentle and non-irritating, making them ideal for first-time skincare users or anyone looking for a low-maintenance, effective routine. Whether you're dealing with puberty breakouts or adult hormonal acne, Blume has you covered.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="56c5d020-9106-40ad-b851-32d374db2df9" class="r-1u2g2qi" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="24e1b55f-894d-4607-97fa-b4b5dcbd7825" aria-controls="replo-:Rmqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-cyjsej"><div data-rid="8cdbc876-0ebf-4dba-b5fe-aba0d71f1d3a" class="r-17fmzq1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What age is Blume suited for?</p></span></div><div data-rid="b8bbadce-de4d-4b41-9886-81b855f65331" class="r-7ivtt3"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-119w8kz" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:Rmqb2:"><div data-rid="5d4e5a86-29e9-40c3-82ec-cd8c18fff1ff" class="r-fzzt4z"><div data-rid="cdfa8134-0c1e-444e-9516-2a74d68a3458" class="r-1grdm6k alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Blume is great for teens, young adults, and anyone with sensitive, acne-prone skin. It can be used for as young as 7 years old, up until 100! Our formulas are gentle and non-irritating, making them ideal for first-time skincare users or anyone looking for a low-maintenance, effective routine. Whether you're dealing with puberty breakouts or adult hormonal acne, Blume has you covered.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="79e406d7-4b6c-44d7-aa79-8ab601c75335" class="r-15ua4mg" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="61d6b805-1077-4acc-87e2-fd8532d7833f" aria-controls="replo-:Rqqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-17kinhw"><div data-rid="e26a4674-986a-4faf-921e-3b45e017fdfd" class="r-ap5o2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Should Meltdown Oil be used as a spot treatment or all over?</p></span></div><div data-rid="ea90be93-21e6-4404-8266-d15e70106482" class="r-19xszpn"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-lk1yzj" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:Rqqb2:"><div data-rid="d8cc8ff5-db23-4e9d-a813-6225d7c31224" class="r-185oe4c"><div data-rid="afa8453b-bf7e-410b-99db-4d07575b43d3" class="r-vr0qid alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>You can use it both ways! Spot treat individual pimples or apply a thin layer all over areas that tend to break out to prevent future flare-ups. It absorbs quickly and layers well under makeup or other skincare. You can also Mix Meltdown Oil into your favorite moisturizer.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="f4c7d7de-6cbe-42c7-b494-f4a10a630bc1" class="r-vah0me" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="085c5ae8-7fec-4936-a639-9b4ef0eec125" aria-controls="replo-:Ruqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-id6iey"><div data-rid="1d97c7f5-30da-4677-bf65-df79845c8dc3" class="r-1ao5ir3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Can I use the Clear Skin Kit while on Accutane?</p></span></div><div data-rid="d428aec4-89ea-4bb8-9529-16c93854e4ed" class="r-1n3tlyi"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1ne374a" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:Ruqb2:"><div data-rid="7b88c22c-f790-466e-80af-771e2e43f7aa" class="r-19uid23"><div data-rid="9500032a-ea3f-4ef6-9306-0c4555cb4f97" class="r-1db59rl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Everyone's skin is different during Accutane, so we recommend checking with your dermatologist first. That said, the Clear Skin Kit is gentle, hydrating, and free of harsh exfoliants — many customers on Accutane have found it helpful for calming and supporting their skin barrier. Always patch test if you’re unsure.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="298ee054-f1b3-4003-bd4b-7b2c7af581a6" class="r-1xdsv2f" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="3cf1d903-a681-4b82-a630-fcaf729ff189" aria-controls="replo-:R12qb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1fpr8zj"><div data-rid="5fd27dd4-a7ec-472c-a705-a44ac74556f1" class="r-iwpdt2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will this actually help my acne or just irritate it more?</p></span></div><div data-rid="20ac1aee-9573-41b0-a1ac-d513813f1138" class="r-8b3fzp"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1qe03l4" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R12qb2:"><div data-rid="eff24c6e-bbf7-4e38-8346-5a3a3a0c8f8d" class="r-yir0te"><div data-rid="c7855b79-a4d2-4207-8fdf-f3730db3b65f" class="r-1id2xrf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">The Clear Skin Kit is derm-tested, non-irritating, and made for sensitive skin — no harsh stripping or stinging here. Thousands of customers have seen real results, often when nothing else worked. It’s formulated to calm inflammation, reduce redness, and support your skin long term.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="df16751b-0074-4985-bd0a-f99719579adb" class="r-1kccfji" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="4acf2e61-bbf4-424e-b9cf-467c913dafcb" aria-controls="replo-:R16qb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-unp77p"><div data-rid="1211dee0-776a-4e53-862f-099f3c679adb" class="r-dwbrte alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is it too oily or greasy?</p></span></div><div data-rid="48f12552-1d06-4f11-b8ed-665b6da34c4c" class="r-19q4kq7"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-34wzvn" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R16qb2:"><div data-rid="c7f01f0c-fb64-4cf5-b0bf-d66a028da4af" class="r-garty"><div data-rid="acd5ca0f-984c-42de-b991-4701a3b2f613" class="r-ufhjlh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Not at all. The formulas are lightweight, fast-absorbing, and balance oil production without clogging pores. In fact, many people with oily or combo skin love it because it helps regulate sebum and keeps their skin feeling fresh — not slick.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="9770d601-8811-47ac-a2b7-b2e2e7f0fe5f" class="r-1f7i2x4" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="3e0251e8-9760-4fdb-aef8-06c68f53d0c2" aria-controls="replo-:R1aqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-q7ad38"><div data-rid="bb25d7f9-939d-4d53-911e-9eb9e13f99f6" class="r-7n3jgm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will it dry out my skin?</p></span></div><div data-rid="46689a64-274f-4a81-ba9b-e76c751cb1fb" class="r-4ob4yh"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-13ss97c" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1aqb2:"><div data-rid="66ae38cc-4c36-4709-8ef1-aff18ff5cfaf" class="r-19j74zt"><div data-rid="3d21bd9d-4841-4d61-92ce-eebd980ec255" class="r-648opc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Nope! The Clear Skin Kit is made with hydrating, skin-loving ingredients that soothe and moisturize. There are no drying alcohols or harsh treatments — just effective botanicals and actives that help clear without compromising your moisture barrier.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c8ec7ef4-521f-48c5-8bf9-036551cf6163" class="r-pd2ryo" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="9095254c-8c28-43c6-a641-2b8acb0204f0" aria-controls="replo-:R1eqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-19spn01"><div data-rid="e7448aa6-c0c9-4ea5-9ed4-f2f9f7a888d0" class="r-n2d4ke alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Does it smell strong or weird?</p></span></div><div data-rid="0d1241d2-de27-4ed0-88b0-3477dcca05a8" class="r-1ao14mp"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1f9adli" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1eqb2:"><div data-rid="06fb5137-d836-486a-88c7-9576451b7797" class="r-1d4o1z1"><div data-rid="6279c565-2944-46f0-a9a8-6370d196563b" class="r-k8swqk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">The scent is light and natural — no overpowering or artificial fragrances. Most people say it smells fresh, clean, and subtle. Plus, all of our scents are from natural essential oils or extracts, and we never use synthetic fragrance.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="6613b82e-6f04-4f01-9f47-933b39e5745b" class="r-1a4xpkp" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="9a211d19-5b90-44d7-8c8b-8df8b48e23e6" aria-controls="replo-:R1iqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1vgys9j"><div data-rid="ccf4ff7e-31f8-457f-8b2d-9060d349cf74" class="r-bd20n9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is it worth the price?</p></span></div><div data-rid="2e6e2cbd-8a8c-4995-97f6-9a4ce786861a" class="r-1ytrp8h"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-g52wzu" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1iqb2:"><div data-rid="96f690ef-b467-44ee-b79b-da0675714d16" class="r-jdeixh"><div data-rid="0d523226-f3d8-4157-8c4a-3ddbcabdd572" class="r-jnvry6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>100%! You're getting a full acne-fighting routine that’s clean, effective, and lasts a long time. Each product is packed with high-quality, active ingredients that you’d typically only find in more expensive treatments — without the markup or harsh chemicals. And if you don’t, we offer a full money back guarantee</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="7567ffed-7a37-4afd-b44c-231d7077929d" class="r-at6ask" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="a6628c78-e4cf-4cad-890a-f3f50e8f983f" aria-controls="replo-:R1mqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-18iqvua"><div data-rid="502af879-8d98-4735-9274-da7686556a6a" class="r-1cpjo91 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will it cause breakouts before it clears them up?</p></span></div><div data-rid="87359b6c-3142-45db-a569-9468b228ec95" class="r-111xpax"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-erw0ne" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1mqb2:"><div data-rid="937b6280-3894-44d3-aed0-4b6f1ea5508a" class="r-1701qfk"><div data-rid="61d73383-0f1b-46f5-87ea-6446a693495e" class="r-ql91tv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Some people may experience a short purge period — but it’s temporary and part of the clearing process. This happens when active ingredients bring clogged pores to the surface faster than usual. Stick with it, and you’ll likely see smoother, calmer skin in a few weeks.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="1a2bbb33-8b44-4f01-b3c9-2b57b46fd012" class="r-3y52xa" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="ff9ff6ca-0fe6-4074-8b9c-ce391b9a59eb" aria-controls="replo-:R1qqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-g6r16f"><div data-rid="420d5c4c-4b70-44c5-864f-39873fb35b9b" class="r-1v4jkz7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How long before I see results?</p></span></div><div data-rid="6059843c-17dd-4dfb-a518-464160b90493" class="r-f5q0ib"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1whbloa" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1qqb2:"><div data-rid="32731eae-b810-4aa3-ba87-d5f4d100d573" class="r-1hwaqw6"><div data-rid="df2aa88e-0d30-4d24-ae91-0dd3028511ce" class="r-swglj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Many users notice a difference in 2–4 weeks, with continued improvements over time! Results can vary depending on your skin type and routine, but consistency is key. Most customers see fewer breakouts, reduced redness, and more balanced skin within the first month. </p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="cd502503-39fc-4f8d-9b73-c612759ba573" class="r-1tqr42" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="fe6e1a33-222c-49c9-bc47-4c07e7016a46" aria-controls="replo-:R1uqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-g3wfdm"><div data-rid="90464154-091c-44ae-a160-d05f07161abc" class="r-1gds322 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Where are your products made?</p></span></div><div data-rid="69688ef0-9345-4639-a511-0149a8d18257" class="r-b9muw0"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-9o49jn" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1uqb2:"><div data-rid="6ceb5aba-bcd1-41c6-b9c7-0b2758b95c49" class="r-1oswuqj"><div data-rid="dc56768d-55e0-40f2-8489-7873a45ba7a4" class="r-4sx6nc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Blume Products are made in Canada and the United States.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="ac450b88-d002-4b6d-9063-41f7236dee07" class="r-10ojjui" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="852f44a8-3679-4697-ab85-1eff38f658fb" aria-controls="replo-:R22qb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-9p0f7i"><div data-rid="71282a66-1ad1-4501-984a-dd98f0b2a590" class="r-17d8m1x alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Are your products cruelty-free, vegan, paraben, sulfate, phthalate, and synthetic fragrance free?</p></span></div><div data-rid="7d6c6bfe-5362-4a55-b779-1ddb72bdaf23" class="r-jiugxk"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-yj58it" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R22qb2:"><div data-rid="a3a4bff7-ed4a-4595-a5df-22dae42c3ed5" class="r-d9p4k4"><div data-rid="03deb1e1-8f57-4e41-a8b4-2a77c5da774d" class="r-6jp5qm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes!</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="4b9d48ca-3b40-4b1a-a2b9-9a5ba828df18" class="r-1loe594" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="1f08222e-af74-4eec-8576-0ab547d59b4f" aria-controls="replo-:R26qb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-18cdi2z"><div data-rid="1fc81ee8-9bc8-4b27-8b12-b04fd87d96af" class="r-1mitll5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Why don’t you include active ingredients in Meltdown Oil?</p></span></div><div data-rid="48b1ddf9-c7f4-45f3-9c36-4646687ea761" class="r-1ot7wlk"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1xvglv2" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R26qb2:"><div data-rid="91a63f78-3886-4ebd-ad52-3c925a4cae71" class="r-12sgx4c"><div data-rid="4f173991-9b0c-4001-a6a2-8fe08edc98f7" class="r-182h5tx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Meltdown Oil uses gentle, anti-inflammatory essential oils to fight acne. These ingredients are a great alternative for sensitive skin, or for those who prefer to use natural ingredients on their skin.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="879e5321-8a6b-40df-ac3e-7d8a0b8c8e52" class="r-1ob6vod" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="7d9c2eaa-e6ff-49a3-aa72-131428f0a707" aria-controls="replo-:R2aqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-rdb3lk"><div data-rid="10d06f9d-5fa3-40d3-94ee-df36061b69c8" class="r-1o56gpb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I’m worried about using oil for my acne, is it comedogenic?</p></span></div><div data-rid="b98482f6-5f58-44c8-bcdf-c099ec278e99" class="r-qr6hh4"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1d0648k" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2aqb2:"><div data-rid="eaa96958-1b83-4e4e-b812-2d4f5861a989" class="r-144uh3j"><div data-rid="ee517706-0f6f-4bc5-a857-1bc812637ac5" class="r-864jvo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The oils used in Meltdown Oil all have comedogenicity ratings below 3. This means that your skin can enjoy the anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial benefits of the essential oils in Meltdown, without worrying about breakouts! Oil can be a result of over-stripping our skin, so adding moisture and oil-based products can prevent your skin from excess oil production.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="659c6eb7-908e-4bb0-9d61-a3ed590e8f19" class="r-17cucmd" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="da9296a6-58dc-4308-953d-75ee407cb276" aria-controls="replo-:R2eqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1n3834h"><div data-rid="1d0343ef-868b-4fd3-85b0-3e277fde67d8" class="r-188514x alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Does the Clear Skin work for hormonal acne?</p></span></div><div data-rid="7e02ea43-6f01-414c-a48e-393deb991965" class="r-295q35"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1vq77ie" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2eqb2:"><div data-rid="d73310f9-bad2-4d6c-8f7f-2367b7d9c8ff" class="r-1k2cjv2"><div data-rid="00c03081-de76-4265-9ba4-1ce03f352be4" class="r-176mnw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes! The Clear Skin Kit targets acne at the root, before it ever comes to head. With a gentle yet deep cleansing system, an anti-inflammatory treatment than your skin can absorb instead of just sit on the surface and hydrating moisturizer. This was made to treat hormonal acne.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="357ead1a-a200-4e92-9b96-8306cddafe4a" class="r-1capxd6" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="e85b2529-2d85-4f48-9a48-175124ffbee7" aria-controls="replo-:R2iqb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1doiv75"><div data-rid="9a2d5046-15f0-43f7-9feb-297057e2a54d" class="r-18uetx2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How long will it take to get my order?</p></span></div><div data-rid="b6bcb5ba-6f2d-4f7e-b2b7-ce41976018d0" class="r-gw2mg"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-vjas4i" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2iqb2:"><div data-rid="61950db7-5b00-458d-90d2-f6f0881637d0" class="r-7eive1"><div data-rid="c7c27910-5a04-4bd9-9507-10fb4cd8ab1c" class="r-2yx38e alchemy-rte"><span sty