y went through - puberty, getting on and off birth control, final exam seasons, stress! No matter what they did, their hormonal acne always came back.</p><br><p>After tons of trial and error (and money down the drain), they started digging into the real root causes of hormonal acne. What they discovered was that most acne products were way too harsh—stripping the skin barrier and throwing hormones even more off balance. Plus, everything was topical, so the treatments they were using couldn’t actually fight hormonal acne that was under the skin. They didn’t want to rely on pills or harsh products like Accutane, so they did their own research.</p><br><p>In their research, they came across black cumin seed oil—an anti-inflammatory, antibacterial powerhouse their mom had used for her own breakouts. Once they started using it, they saw a noticeable difference in their skin. That one discovery sparked the creation of The Clear Skin Kit, developed alongside dermatologists and specifically designed to soothe, balance, and heal hormonal acne without the irritation. What they learned was that Black Cumin Seed Oil is an oil that can penetrate beyond the top layer of your skin, and fight hormonal acne before it ever comes to a head, unlike other acne treatments.</p><br><br></span></div><button data-rid="291f9ac9-350f-4ef9-a713-ef7174e3b0de" tabindex="0" role="link" class="text r-ac0qo7 alchemy-rte"><div data-rid="0df6a828-4a68-49ab-b0a4-3a6c9a6fb84d" class="r-56mlpe alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>GET YOUR CLEAR SKIN KIT</p></span></div></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="1a26c140-38d7-4cd5-9f53-50c95baba745" data-alchemy-url-hashmark="reviews" tabindex="-1" id="reviews" data-alchemy-url-hashmark-ignore="true" class="r-6cfo6"><div data-rid="2d676d35-2ea9-4296-a722-56c7d5b39154" class="r-1tztqj" data-alchemy-prerendered-component-id="2d676d35-2ea9-4296-a722-56c7d5b39154">{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-begin{%- endcomment -%}<div style="width:1